yle=\"font-size:18.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">“Unsecured\r\nFinancing Alternatives” <o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\ntext-align:center;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">23<sup>rd</sup>\r\nFebruary, 2022 | 14:00 to 17:00 hrs. | Virtual Event<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(32, 33, 36); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Finance is the elixir that&nbsp;assists<b> </b>and allows businesses\r\nto take advantage of opportunities to grow. Of late, it’s been noticed that the\r\nindustry has been </span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">finding\r\nit difficult to solve the increasing challenges of the availability and\r\nmanagement of Working Capital<span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 36); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\nfunds which is </span>an important function of financial management<span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 36); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"> as also the </span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.15pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">lifeblood of every\r\norganization.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.15pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(32, 33, 36); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">ACMA has been deliberating on this and were\r\nworking on ways to find out alternate channels of financing for our\r\nmembers.&nbsp; I am happy to inform that we\r\nhave been able to find out three interesting sources addressing all t</span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.15pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">hree key components of working capital, viz., Accounts\r\nPayables, Accounts Receivables and Inventory, which analysts examine for clues\r\nto a company’s financial soundness and operational efficiency.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(32, 33, 36); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(32, 33, 36); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">The unique feature of these sources is that\r\nthese sources of working capital debt do not need to be secured by way of a\r\ncollateral.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(32, 33, 36); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">In an\r\neffort to disseminate these 3 sources amongst our members to enable them take\r\nbenefit of, ACMA is organizing its <b>1<sup>st</sup>\r\nNational CFOs Summit</b> on the topic <b>“Unsecured\r\nFinancing Alternative”</b> on <b>23<sup>rd</sup>\r\nFebruary, 2022 from 1400 hrs.- 1700 hrs</b>. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">The CFOs\r\nSummit aims to deliberate on the following key topics :</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.75in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Symbol;\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Session I- Mezz Financing / Structured Debt<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\">o<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\