·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Session III- Supplier Payable Financing<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\">o<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Speaker-<o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0in; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1.75in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Wingdings;\">§<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Mr.Ram Kewalramani, Co-Founder &amp; MD, CredAble</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1.75in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p><br></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">We invite\r\nACMA members Companies to be a part of this new initiative by filling the below\r\nlink &amp; nominate yourself with your Colleagues, Team Members, Senior\r\nManagement &amp; Suppliers <span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">to recalibrate and\r\nstay relevant.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Registration Link-</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp; <a href=\"https://forms.gle/NbviXgosQ7Z7bvGM7\">https://forms.gle/NbviXgosQ7Z7bvGM7</a>\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1.75in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Further,\r\nMembers can also utilize this virtual platform as a <b>“Branding Opportunity”</b> as we have worked a special package for\r\nDigital Co-Sponsorship &amp; the benefits that would accrue to Co-sponsors are\r\nmentioned below:</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p><br></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 115%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol;\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Digital Co-Sponsorship Fee:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 115%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\">o<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Rs. 50,000/-(For Members)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 1in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 115%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: &quot;Courier New&quot;;\">o<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">Rs. 75,000/- (For Non-Members)<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.5in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; line-height: 115%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Symbol;\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"fo