fasteners.com,asb@victora.co.in,kc@kusalava.com,tushar@sbapl.com,utkarsh@sbapl.com,vaishali@alliedtransmission.in,parth@bansalpresses.com,rajivnazareth@alfengineering.com,simar@jsg.asia,HDGANDHI@MUTUALAUTOMOTIVE.IN,harshal.gandhi@aispl.co,harjai@ballkings.com,ashwinnazareth@alfengineering.com,malaikadsouza@alfengineering.com,gauriunnithan@sankar.com,rishi.sujan@polyrubplastics.com,sharan.sujan@megarubbertech.com,radhika@sellowrap.com,MDOFFICE@SUPERSCREWS.COM,arpit@precisionautowares.net,aniket.chopda@smet.co.in,pathik@microsignproducts.com,sushen.mittal@aartisteelsltd.com,varunbansal@jayashreepolymers.com,jatin@rukmanudyog.com,rhea@endurance.co.in,rohan@endurance.co.in,mukulsareen@doctorrust.com,piyushmunot@klassicwheels.com,nandan@nandangroup.com,varun@nandangroup.com,ankit.dhiman@acma.in', NULL, NULL, 'sapna.vijh@acma.in', 'Forthcoming Premier events of ACMA in physical mode on 23-24 March, 2022 ( ATPSE_EV_iAutoConnect) at India  Expo Centre & Mart, Greater Noida, India', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right; \"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">19th February, 2022</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Dear\r\nMember,</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Forthcoming Premier\r\nevents of ACMA in physical mode</span></u></b><u><o:p></o:p></u></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">23 – 24 March, 2022<o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">India Expo Centre &amp;\r\nMart, Greater Noida, India<o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">I\r\nam pleased to inform you that after a gap of almost 2 years, ACMA is organizing\r\nevents in physical mode. Last week, Government of India has announced\r\nrelaxation of norms for international travelers and we are optimistic about\r\ncommencement of regular flights by end of February.<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Encouraged\r\nby these positive developments, we are organizing three premier events of ACMA\r\ntogether – &nbsp;the Auto Technology Partnership Summit &amp; Expo, the EV\r\n&amp; Components Expo and &nbsp;the iAutoConnect on 23<sup>rd</sup><span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>&amp; 24<sup>th</sup><span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>March, 2022 at India Expo Centre &amp;\r\nMart, Greater Noida, India.<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 25px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">All\r\ndetails pertinent to these events are available with regular updates on the\r\nwebsite:<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><a href=\"http://www.acmaevents.in\" target=\"_blank\"><b><u>www.acmaevents.in</u></b></a></p><p><img src=\"https://www.acma.in/uploads/otherdocmanager/ATPSE_EV_iAutoConnect_www.acmaevents.in.jpg\" style=\"width: 680px;\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">We\r\nhave extended the last date for submission of confirmation for participation of\r\nthese events to 28<sup>th</sup><span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span>February,\r\n2022. The subsidised cost of participation and other details remain the same.</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12.0pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">I\r\nlook forward to your confirmation for participation at this unique opportunity\r\nof engaging with the global stakeholders.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 21.3333px;\">Thank you,</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 21.3333px;\"><br></span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right; \"><font face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 21.3333px;\">Secretary</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><font face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 21.3333px;\">ACMA/2021-2022/80</span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right; \"><font face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 21.3333px;\"><br></span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 21.3333px;\"><br></span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"Arial, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 21.3333px;\"><br></span></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><br></span><o:p></o:p></p>', '', '2022-02-19 11:29:51');
