topfasteners.com,asb@victora.co.in,kc@kusalava.com,tushar@sbapl.com,utkarsh@sbapl.com,vaishali@alliedtransmission.in,parth@bansalpresses.com,rajivnazareth@alfengineering.com,simar@jsg.asia,HDGANDHI@MUTUALAUTOMOTIVE.IN,harshal.gandhi@aispl.co,harjai@ballkings.com,ashwinnazareth@alfengineering.com,malaikadsouza@alfengineering.com,gauriunnithan@sankar.com,rishi.sujan@polyrubplastics.com,sharan.sujan@megarubbertech.com,radhika@sellowrap.com,MDOFFICE@SUPERSCREWS.COM,arpit@precisionautowares.net,aniket.chopda@smet.co.in,pathik@microsignproducts.com,sushen.mittal@aartisteelsltd.com,varunbansal@jayashreepolymers.com,jatin@rukmanudyog.com,rhea@endurance.co.in,rohan@endurance.co.in,mukulsareen@doctorrust.com,piyushmunot@klassicwheels.com,nandan@nandangroup.com,varun@nandangroup.com,chetan.singh@webeesocial.com,shubham.ahlawat@webeesocial.com,anurag.joshi@webeesocial.com,upender.singh@acma.in,ankit.dhiman@acma.in,shubhendu.jha@webeesocial.com', NULL, NULL, 'sapna.vijh@acma.in', 'Forthcoming Premier events of ACMA in physical mode on 23-24 March, 2022 ( ATPSE_EV_iAutoConnect) at India Expo Centre & Mart, Greater Noida, India', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><a name=\"_MailOriginal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F497D\">19<sup>th</sup>\r\nFebruary, 2022<o:p></o:p></span></a></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\">Dear Member,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\">Forthcoming Premier\r\nevents of ACMA in physical mode</span></u></b><u><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\"><o:p></o:p></span></u></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\">23 – 24 March, 2022<o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\">India Expo Centre\r\n&amp; Mart, Greater Noida, India<o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\">I am pleased to inform\r\nyou that after a gap of almost 2 years, ACMA is organizing events in physical\r\nmode. Last week, Government of India has announced relaxation of norms for\r\ninternational travelers and we are optimistic about commencement of regular flights\r\nby end of February.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\">Encouraged by these\r\npositive developments, we are organizing three premier events of ACMA together\r\n– &nbsp;the Auto Technology Partnership Summit &amp; Expo, the EV &amp;\r\nComponents Expo and &nbsp;the iAutoConnect on 23<sup>rd</sup>&nbsp;&amp; 24<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;March,\r\n2022 at India Expo Centre &amp; Mart, Greater Noida, India.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\">All details pertinent\r\nto these events are available with regular updates on the website:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://www.acmaevents.in/\" target=\"_blank\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\r\n&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:windowtext\">www.acmaevents.in</span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\">We have extended the\r\nlast date for submission of confirmation for participation of these events to\r\n28<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;February, 2022. The subsidised cost of participation and\r\nother details remain the same.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\"><br>\r\nI look forward to your confirmation for participation at this unique\r\nopportunity of engaging with the global stakeholders.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F497D\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F497D\">Thanking\r\nYou, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F497D\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-right:.5in\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F497D\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\">SECRETARY&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#1F497D\">ACMA/2021-2022/80<o:p></o:p></span></p>', 'ATPSE_EV_iAutoConnect_www.acmaevents.in.jpg', '2022-02-19 12:15:03');
