odia@jayahind.com,shubham.ahlawat@webeesocial.com,chetan.singh@webeesocial.com,upender.singh@acma.in', NULL, NULL, 'sapna.vijh@acma.in', 'Forthcoming Premier events of ACMA in physical mode on 23-24 March, 2022 (ATPSE_EV_iAutoConnect) at India Expo Centre & Mart, Greater Noida, India', '<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpFirst\" align=\"right\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;\r\nmso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:right;line-height:\r\n15.0pt\"><a name=\"m_-6094765704035005252__MailOriginal\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\">19<sup>th</sup> February,\r\n2022</span></a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Dear Member,</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;\r\nmso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:\r\n15.0pt\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Forthcoming Premier events of ACMA in physical mode</span></u></b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;\r\nmso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:\r\n15.0pt\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">23 – 24 March, 2022</span></u></b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;\r\nmso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:\r\n15.0pt\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">India Expo Centre &amp; Mart, Greater Noida, India</span></u></b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></b><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">I am pleased to inform you that\r\nafter a gap of almost 2 years, ACMA is organizing events in physical mode. Last\r\nweek, Government of India has announced relaxation of norms for international\r\ntravelers and we are optimistic about commencement of regular flights by end of\r\nFebruary.&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Encouraged by these positive\r\ndevelopments, we are organizing three premier events of ACMA together –\r\n&nbsp;the Auto Technology Partnership Summit &amp; Expo, the EV &amp;\r\nComponents Expo and &nbsp;the iAutoConnect on 23<sup>rd</sup>&nbsp;&amp; 24<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;March,\r\n2022 at India Expo Centre &amp; Mart, Greater Noida, India.&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">All details pertinent to these\r\nevents are available with regular updates on the website:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://url3385.acma.in/ls/click?upn=lxpNgeg34x3KhrQa9NUM8dw-2F4grZb2N4U-2BIiadU9lOTwP1Za0nqA0c1vqATfeyJ-2BV4YS_k0kpSMzHRwqJhshwqVW3OjRXK9nBkgDUrO2G3NRUYLKKx-2BoC5QmonpLkNZgozYTZw-2F82BR3dasTvIuMVsqZ8nZRBK2aC5j17zy-2Fl2p246WD0IS-2FB9I61NglFGLsDUgRLusESvT52x65ziTRDE4FEd3qlbw9EesXamDPqurhCLdCvTkIPCJ7C9S22pIe4RWDKZcTBq3-2B5X4QUUofClud-2FsQ-3D-3D\" target=\"_blank\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:black\">www.acmaevents.in</span></b></a><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">We have extended the last date for\r\nsubmission of confirmation for participation of these events to <b><u>28<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;February,\r\n2022</u></b>. The subsidised cost of participation and other details remain the\r\nsame.</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\"><br>\r\nI look forward to your confirmation for participation at this unique\r\nopportunity of engaging with the global stakeholders.</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Thanking You, </span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-right:.5in;\r\nmso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"right\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;\r\nmso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:right;line-height:\r\n15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">SECRETARY&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">ACMA/2021-2022/80</span><br></p>', 'ATPSE_EV_iAutoConnect_www.acmaevents.in.jpg', '2022-02-21 10:15:10');
