auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;\r\n  mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:\r\n  15.0pt\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Forthcoming Premier events of ACMA in physical mode</span></u></b><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;\r\n  mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:\r\n  15.0pt\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">23 – 24 March, 2022</span></u></b><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;\r\n  mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:center;mso-line-height-alt:\r\n  15.0pt\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size: 16pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">India Expo Centre &amp; Mart, Greater Noida, India</span></u></b><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n  auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></b><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n  auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">I am pleased to inform you that\r\n  after a gap of almost 2 years, ACMA is organizing events in physical mode.\r\n  Last week, Government of India has announced relaxation of norms for\r\n  international travelers and we are optimistic about commencement of regular\r\n  flights by end of February.&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n  auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n  auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Encouraged by these positive\r\n  developments, we are organizing three premier events of ACMA together –\r\n  &nbsp;the Auto Technology Partnership Summit &amp; Expo, the EV &amp;\r\n  Components Expo and &nbsp;the iAutoConnect on 23<sup>rd</sup>&nbsp;&amp; 24<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;March,\r\n  2022 at India Expo Centre &amp; Mart, Greater Noida, India.&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n  auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n  auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">All details pertinent to these\r\n  events are available with regular updates on the website:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://url3385.acma.in/ls/click?upn=lxpNgeg34x3KhrQa9NUM8dw-2F4grZb2N4U-2BIiadU9lOTwP1Za0nqA0c1vqATfeyJ-2BV4YS_k0kpSMzHRwqJhshwqVW3OjRXK9nBkgDUrO2G3NRUYLKKx-2BoC5QmonpLkNZgozYTZw-2F82BR3dasTvIuMVsqZ8nZRBK2aC5j17zy-2Fl2p246WD0IS-2FB9I61NglFGLsDUgRLusESvT52x65ziTRDE4FEd3qlbw9EesXamDPqurhCLdCvTkIPCJ7C9S22pIe4RWDKZcTBq3-2B5X4QUUofClud-2FsQ-3D-3D\" target=\"_blank\"><b><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n  color:black\">www.acmaevents.in</span></b></a><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n  auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n  auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">We have extended the last date\r\n  for submission of confirmation for participation of these events to <b><u>28<sup>th</sup>&nbsp;February,\r\n  2022</u></b>. The subsidised cost of participation and other details remain\r\n  the same.</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n  auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\"><br>\r\n  I look forward to your confirmation for participation at this unique\r\n  opportunity of engaging with the global stakeholders.</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n  auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n  auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Thanking You, </span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n  auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;margin-right:\r\n  .5in;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"right\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;\r\n  mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;mso-add-space:auto;text-align:right;line-height:\r\n  15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">SECRETARY&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\r\n  auto;mso-add-space:auto;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">ACMA/2021-2022/80</span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n</tbody></table><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img border=\"0\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" id=\"_x0000_i1025\" src=\"http://url3385.acma.in/wf/open?upn=gtHMQ-2F7FCLhspjirEtwbPUcDK0HoaUlitLT0Iuz6Tc58EuuGnCBigChoyHl-2BVuNm-2BtKJV88EiXPefxtoRn0mlY24D-2FAFmALH-2F5EvuKro0Oi8B30-2BQNEdteNdFi1e1oMJLrewKP4ahHRG4ts7eH7fCXZgkwbgIsgUsD1v7Ub4MokJRxxbXV0MCEY9xaIjgB-2FAb3VgxWaUyT3S4zfIoESpiP2ttkiTVTVjY-2BQW7A29uP0-3D\"><o:p></o:p></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>', 'ATPSE_EV_iAutoConnect_www.acmaevents.in.jpg', '2022-02-21 13:02:30');
