0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;background:aqua;mso-highlight:aqua\">Online Payment\r\nTransaction -: </span></u></b><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#7030A0\"><a href=\"https://www.acma.in/payment-online.php\"><span style=\"color:#7030A0\">https://</span></a><a href=\"https://www.acma.in/payment-online.php\"><span style=\"color:#7030A0\">www.acma.in/payment-online.php</span></a></span></b></span><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;color:#C00000\">While making the payment please put 0000\r\n(Zero) in Tax Invoice No. column while processing for the payment. Please mail\r\nus the screen shot of the payment </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#C00000\">transaction</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;color:#C00000\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\r\n10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#C00000\">at the email id’s given on the reply\r\nform</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;color:#C00000\"> to cross\r\ncheck it.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:15.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Interested\r\ncompanies are requested to send their confirm participation through <b>Annexure I</b> along with <b><u>full\r\npayment to ACMA</u></b>, to enable us to block your seat for the participation.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:15.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\"><br></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:15.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">We look forward to\r\nreceiving your urgent confirmation to join this unique event, as there is lot\r\nof interest from all the stake holders to participate at the Expo.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Kind regards,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&n