>\r\n    <td><![endif]>\r\n    <div>\r\n    <p class=MsoNormal><b style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><span lang=EN-US\r\n    style=\'font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\"Book Antiqua\",serif;\r\n    background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow\'>New Initiative</span></b><b\r\n    style=\'mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\'><span lang=EN-US style=\'font-size:12.0pt;\r\n    line-height:107%;font-family:\"Book Antiqua\",serif\'><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <![if !mso]></td>\r\n   </tr>\r\n  </table>\r\n  <![endif]></v:textbox>\r\n <w:wrap type=\"square\" anchorx=\"margin\"/>\r\n</v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><!--[endif]--><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-language:\r\nKO\">To: All Members</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-language:\r\nKO\"><br></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><b style=\"background-color: transparent;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-fareast-language:KO\">Dear Member,</span></b><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-fareast-language:KO\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-font-style:italic\">1<sup>st </sup>ACMA FARM\r\nEquipment &amp; Implements Localisation Expo (AFEILE)</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-fareast-language:JA\">Radisson Blu, </span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:JA\">Ferozepur Road, Ludhiana (Punjab)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">6<sup>th</sup> &amp; 7<sup>th</sup> April, 2022 :\r\n10.00 a.m. to 6.30 p.m.</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1F497D;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:2.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">Continuing with our efforts to\r\n</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;\r\nmso-fareast-language:JA\">enhance and engage in the business linkages within the\r\nsupply system at different tiers and also to encourage companies to look at new\r\nbusiness potential in terms of new technology, quality, cost, delivery and\r\ncapacity utilization, ACMA Northern Region &amp; </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:JA\">OEM Sub Pillar of </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA\">the Business Development </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;\r\nmso-fareast-language:JA\">Pillar</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:JA\"> of ACMA, are jointly organizing\r\nthe First-ever FARM Equipment &amp; Implements Localisation Expo at Ludhiana, Punjab.\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;\r\nmso-fareast-language:JA\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">Considering the huge\r\npotential in Punjab for the FARM Equipments &amp; Implements, we are pleased to\r\nannounce the <b>1<sup>st</sup> ACMA FARM\r\nEquipment &amp; Implements Localisation Expo</b> <b>in Ludhiana </b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:JA\">on 6<sup>th</sup> – 7<sup>th</sup>\r\nApril 2022 </span></b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:JA;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">at</span><u><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA\"> </span></u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">Radisson Blu,\r\nFerozepur Road, Ludhiana (Punjab)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-IN\">.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify\"><b><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA\">&nbsp;</span></u></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-fareast-language:JA\">The key objective of the\r\nevent is to provide a platform to :<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n     justify;line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-fareast-language:JA\">Tier-I companies\r\n     to display the components for which they look for both Buyers/ Suppliers. <o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-fareast-language:JA\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:5.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-fareast-language:JA\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n     justify;line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-fareast-language:JA\">For Tier-2/3\r\n     companies to showcase their capabilities and display components for which\r\n     they need buyers and explore new opportunities<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;page-break-after:avoid\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:5.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;page-break-after:avoid\"><u><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-fareast-language:JA\">The Tier-1 companies to be represented by purchasing\r\nteam as well.<o:p></o:p></span></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;page-break-after:avoid\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:JA\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;page-break-after:avoid\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:JA\">We will be inviting senior and\r\nmiddle level sourcing &amp; technical teams from the OEMs, Tier-1s and IPOs\r\nfrom all over the country to visit the exhibition and to interact with\r\nexhibitors/members.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;page-break-after:avoid\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:JA\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA\">We expect around 45–50 component manufacturing companies from all over\r\nIndia to participate at this special Event.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:JA\">Who Can Participate</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-list:l2 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Auto Component Manufacturers (both ACMA Members\r\n&amp; Non-Members)<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-list:l2 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Farm Equipment<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-list:l2 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span class=\"mgabyb\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span class=\"mgabyb\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif\">Off-highway Vehicle Industry<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-18.0pt;\r\nmso-list:l2 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\nWingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span class=\"mgabyb\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif\">Earth Moving &amp; Construction Equipment</span></span><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:JA\">Cost of participation &amp;\r\nFacilities:</span></u></b><b><u><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-