Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n  mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></b></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span class=\"acopre\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\n  mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n  mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Anmol Jain<o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span class=\"acopre\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\n  mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n  mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Co-chairman, Pillar I &amp;<o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;line-height:\r\n  normal\"><span class=\"acopre\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\n  mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\n  mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Northern Region<o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n</tbody></table><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\ntext-align:right;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-fareast-language:KO\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\ntext-align:right;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-fareast-language:KO\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\ntext-align:right;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-fareast-language:KO\">24<sup>th</sup> February 2022<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-fareast-language:KO\">To: All Members<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-fareast-language:KO\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-fareast-language:KO\">Dear Member,<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial;mso-fareast-language:KO\">&nbsp;</span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-bidi-font-style:italic\">1<sup>st </sup>ACMA FARM\r\nEquipment &amp; Implements Localisation Expo (AFEILE)</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-fareast-language:JA\">Radisson Blu, </span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:JA\">Ferozepur Road, Ludhiana (Punjab)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormalCxSpMiddle\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB\">6<sup>th</sup> &amp; 7<sup>th</sup> April, 2022 :\r\n10.00 a.m. to 6.30 p.m.</span></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;color:#1F497D;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:2.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">Continuing with our efforts to </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA\">enhance and engage in the business linkages within the supply system at\r\ndifferent tiers and also to encourage companies to look at new business\r\npotential in terms of new technology, quality, cost, delivery and capacity\r\nutilization, ACMA Northern Region &amp; </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:JA\">OEM Sub Pillar of </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA\">the Business Development </span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;\r\nmso-fareast-language:JA\">Pillar</span><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:JA\"> of ACMA, are jointly organizing\r\nthe First-ever FARM Equipment &amp; Implements Localisation Expo at Ludhiana, Punjab.\r\n<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;\r\nmso-fareast-language:JA\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">Considering the huge potential in Punjab for the\r\nFARM Equipments &amp; Implements, we are pleased to announce the <b>1<sup>st</sup> ACMA FARM Equipment &amp;\r\nImplements Localisation Expo</b> <b>in\r\nLudhiana </b></span><b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:JA\">on 6<sup>th</sup> – 7<sup>th</sup>\r\nApril 2022 </span></b><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:JA;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">at</span><u><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA\"> </span></u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Tahoma\">Radisson Blu, Ferozepur Road,\r\nLudhiana (Punjab)</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif\">.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-fareast-language:JA\">&nbsp;</span></u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-fareast-language:JA\">The key objective of the event is to provide a\r\nplatform to :<o:p></o:p></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n     justify;line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     Batang;mso-fareast-language:JA\">Tier-I companies to display the components\r\n     for which they look for both Buyers/ Suppliers. <o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-fareast-language:JA\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:5.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-fareast-language:JA\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0cm\" type=\"disc\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\n     justify;line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     Batang;mso-fareast-language:JA\">For Tier-2/3 companies to showcase their\r\n     capabilities and display components for which they need buyers and explore\r\n     new opportunities<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;page-break-after:avoid\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:5.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Batang;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:\r\nJA\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;page-break-after:avoid\"><u><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:\r\n107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-fareast-language:JA\">The Tier-1 companies to be represented by purchasing\r\nteam as well.<o:p></o:p></span></u></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;page-break-after:avoid\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:JA\">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;page-break-after:avoid\"><span lang=\"EN-GB\" style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Batang;\r\nmso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-fareast-language:JA\">We will be inviting senior and\r\nmiddle level sourcing &amp; technical teams from the OEMs, Tier-1s and IPOs\r\nfrom all over the country to visit the exhibition and to interact with\r\nexhibitors/members.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-