hp\"><span style=\"color:#7030A0\">https://</span></a><a href=\"https://www.acma.in/payment-online.php\"><span style=\"color:#7030A0\">www.acma.in/payment-online.php</span></a></span></b></span><span class=\"MsoHyperlink\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Arial\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;\r\ncolor:#C00000\">While making the payment please put 0000 (Zero) in Tax Invoice\r\nNo. column while processing for the payment. Please mail us the screen shot of\r\nthe payment </span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;\r\nline-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\r\ncolor:#C00000\">transaction</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;color:#C00000\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;color:#C00000\">at the email\r\nid’s given on the reply form</span><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;color:#C00000\"> to\r\ncross check it.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Interested\r\ncompanies are requested to send their confirm participation through <b>Annexure I</b> along with <b><u>full\r\npayment to ACMA</u></b>, to enable us to block your seat for the participation.</span><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:15.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">We look forward to\r\nreceiving your urgent confirmation to join this unique event, as there is lot\r\nof interest from all the stake holders to participate at the Expo.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">Kind regards,<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:\r\n12.0pt;line-height:107%;font-family:&quot;Book Antiqua&quot;,serif;mso-bidi-font-family:\r\nArial\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Yours sincerely, <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shapetype\r\n id=\"_x0000_t75\" coordsize=\"21600,21600\" o:spt=\"75\" o:preferrelative=\"t\"\r\n path=\"m@4@5l@4@11@9@11@9@5xe\" filled=\"f\" stroked=\"f\">\r\n <v:stroke joinstyle=\"miter\"/>\r\n <v:formulas>\r\n  <v:f eqn=\"if lineDrawn pixelLineWidth 0\"/>\